Reports --> New Reports --> Select a Report Type : Cases --> Start Report --> Outline --> Group Rows: Case Reason | Columns (Add): Account Name, Subject 
--> From Fields "Number of SolarBots" drag and drop in columns --> Columns : Add Bucked Columns --> Field : Number of SolarBots, Bucket Name : SolarBot Ownership 
1. Range = 0, Bucket = No SolarBots --> Add
2. Range = 3, Bucket = Some SolarBots
3. Bucket = Several SolarBots --> Apply
--> Drag and drop "SolarBot OwnerShip" to Group Rows
--> Deselect : Row Counts / Subtotals / Grand Total --> Save & Run --> Report Name : Top Case Drivers by SolarBot Ownership --> 
Folder : SolarBot Support Reports --> Save

Reports --> New Reports --> Select a Report Type : SolarBots and Status Data --> Start Report --> Outline --> Group Rows: Status Date | 
Columns : Panel Temperature / Percent Obscured / Kilowatt Hours
--> Deselect : Row Counts / Detail Rows / Subtotals / Grand Total --> Save & Run --> Report Name : SolarBot Status Averages --> 
Folder : SolarBot Support Reports --> Status Reports --> Select Folder --> Save
